Psionicists are mental-discipline casters trained to access and manipulate cognitive architecture directly.
Three ancestral lineages converge: the Spirebound Conclave's Pale Ledger faction, the Void Citadel's recurrence technology, and ambient institutional cognitive traditions.
The Pale Ledger lineage is the most technically documented, focused on memory encoding, behavioral dispositions, and direct cognitive access.
Core capability: reaching past surface resistance into the architecture of will itself.
Combat role is mental-domain caster with abilities targeting cognition, memory, and willpower.
Knowledge of cognitive architecture serves both offense and defense equally.
Psionicists operate in persistent legal ambiguity across the five cities, not fully licensed or outlawed.
All five cities have attempted civic oversight of psionicist institutions. None have fully succeeded.
The Egomancer class is the remort path for Psionicists who commit to the imposition doctrine.
The tradition self-identifies as a counter-institution to institutional cognitive control.
